# Privacy Policy

**Effective Date:** 2025-06-03  
**Application Name:** BookGurus

## 1. Overview

This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our mobile application.

We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data.

## 2. Information We Collect

### 2.1. Camera Access
- Our app requires access to your device's camera for barcode scanning purposes.
- We do not store or transmit any images or video from your camera.
- The scanning process is done locally on your device.

### 2.2. No Personal Information Collected
- We do not collect, store, or share any personal information such as name, email, phone number, or location.
- No user accounts or login information are required to use the app.

### 2.3. Device Information
- We do not collect any device identifiers or other metadata.

## 3. Data Usage

- The data from barcode scanning is processed locally and not transmitted to any servers.
- No data is stored or analyzed outside the app.

## 4. Third-Party Services

- Our app does not use any third-party analytics, ads, or tracking services.

## 5. Data Security

- As no personal data is collected, no storage or transmission of sensitive information occurs.
- The app only uses necessary permissions to function (camera access).

## 6. Childrenâ€™s Privacy

- The application does not target children and does not knowingly collect information from children under 13 years of age.

## 7. Changes to This Privacy Policy

- We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be effective upon posting the updated policy.

## 8. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, you can contact us at:

**Email:** info@bookgurus.com
